CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1951, pg. 12, reads: "Hostess Party - A gala affair, given by the Grand Court of Deliberation AAOO Daughters of Sphinx, a week ago Sunday, at the YWCA, honored the above matrons. Left to right: S. G. M. Sister Esther Greene, OES; S. V. Matron Myrtle Gilbert, S. G. M. Ellen Poole, G. D. Mary Brown and S. G. M. Lula Lane. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of Grand Court of Deliberation, Daughters of Sphinx, from left: Esther Greene, Myrtle Gilbert, Ellen Poole, Mary Brown, and Lula Lane, posed behind table with floral arrangement in YWCA
